{"tid":1940939,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［神秘撚入］聖經博物館裡的「死海古卷」全都是贗品","createTime":"2020-03-24T06:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T09:14:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b3c5464ede7fabd92bdf144d1cf15c744ef34d","tid":1940939,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"在聖經博物館（The Museum of the Bible）的四樓，有一項占地頗廣的常設展，訴說著古老的聖經如何成為全世界最熱門書籍的故事。展示區中央一處有溫暖燈光照耀的聖龕，展示了這間博物館最珍貴的某幾件財產：死海古卷（Dead Sea Scrolls）的破片，是包括希伯來聖經現存已知最古老抄本在內的古老文本。<br />\n<br />\n但現在，這間位於華盛頓特區的博物館已經確認了有關這些碎片真實與否的苦澀真相。3月13日，由聖經博物館贊助的獨立研究團隊宣布，該博物館蒐藏的16片死海古卷碎片，全都是現代製作的贗品，並長期愚弄了外界的蒐藏家、博物館創辦人，以及幾位世界頂尖的聖經學者。在由博物館主辦的學術研討會上，博物館人員揭開了這項發現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.natgeomedia.com/history/article/content-10867.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natgeomedia.com%2Fhistory%2Farticle%2Fcontent-10867.html&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1lhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=4f579e2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.natgeomedia.com/history/article/content-10867.html</a><br />\n<br />\n炒到應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de60e883433f22a41e7db4941ec370b31d75f024","tid":1940939,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"SEELE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c810148a2c176a60a27ced6c758ed3c880341bc6","tid":1940939,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"真果d收埋曬啦<br />\n<br />\n真相唔比得公眾知㗎<br />\n<br />\n例如世界上最大地主係耶教"},{"pid":"0911c3e10ea4a290e613cad0997079277f7b51fc","tid":1940